weekly_watchlist.title: Weekly Watchlist
weekly_watchlist.description: Can't decide which Tubi title to watch first? Try one of this week's top picks.

307762.title: The Three Musketeers
307762.description: In this classic tale of friendship and heroism, a young, aspiring musketeer must team up with three legendary fighters to save France.

380523.title: Frankie & Alice
380523.description: Inspired by a true story, a '70s go-go dancer with multiple personality disorder begins seeing a psychotherapist in an attempt to regain stability.

385507.title: Empire State
385507.description: When two friends attempt to rob an armored car depository containing millions, they must elude a veteran NYPD detective and angry local crime bosses.

437181.title: Red Cliff
437181.description: The legendary battle that heralded the end of the Han Dynasty and changed the face of China forever comes to life in this epic historical drama.

437409.title: George A. Romero's Survival of the Dead
437409.description: Off the coast of Delaware, two families are locked in a power struggle with different approaches to tackling their nightmarish, zombie-ruled world.

437411.title: Rubber
437411.description: An abandoned tire inexplicably comes to life, possessing terrifying power that can destroy anything. When his attention turns to humans, chaos reigns.

438043.title: Filth
438043.description: A scheming detective drowning in mad plots, drugs, alcohol and sexually abusive relationships becomes mentally unstable while working a murder case.

453775.title: Tim & Eric's Billion Dollar Movie
453775.description: After wasting their movie's billion-dollar budget, Tim and Eric take a job rehabilitating a bankrupt mall full of eccentric characters.

453777.title: Conan O'Brien: Cant Stop
453777.description: The comedian embarks on a 32-city tour following his very public exit from the Tonight Show, in this intimate portrait of an artist at the crossroads.

460947.title: Chawz
460947.description: A rookie cop discovers a mutant boar, with a voracious appetite for human flesh, is responsible for a series of gruesome murders in a Korean village.

460957.title: Murder Party
460957.description: A luckless loser shows up at a Halloween party, and finds himself at the mercy of strangers who want to murder him for the sake of art.

462812.title: Julia
462812.description: After a chance encounter, a struggling alcoholic gets embroiled in a plot to help kidnap a woman’s son that escalates far beyond her expectations.

465428.title: Gods of Egypt
465428.description: A mortal tries to save the world and his own true love by joining with a powerful god in an epic battle against his rival, the deadly god of darkness.

469821.title: Fear
469821.description: A teenage girl’s dream crush on an older man, whom even her family approves of, turns terrifying when he reveals he’s an obsessed, psychopath stalker.

511159.title: Stage Fright
511159.description: A starry-eyed teenager aiming for Broadway works in the kitchen at a snobby arts camp, where a maniac killer who hates musicals is on the loose.

512448.title: New Jack City
512448.description: Two streetwise cops embark on the riskiest mission of their careers when they go undercover to bust a ruthless drug kingpin reigning over Harlem.

516859.title: The Last Witch Hunter
516859.description: A fearless, immortal witch hunter ends up in a ferocious battle with supernatural enemies as he fights to save the human race from evil.

522072.title: Silent Hill
522072.description: A mother desperately searches for her adopted daughter through a town that’s been possessed by an evil force. Can she find her in time?

528599.title: Takers
528599.description: High-octane thriller about a group of notorious criminals whose streak of untraceable bank heists may come to an end thanks to a hardcore detective.

539272.title: Evil Dead
539272.description: This update to the classic horror flick finds five friends in a cabin, about to unlock the curses that live inside the Book of the Dead.

545512.title: Blade II
545512.description: Blade, the vampire-human hybrid, joins forces with a highly-skilled team of vampires to vanquish a new race of super vampires out for Armageddon.

550824.title: The Hunger Games
550824.description: In a dystopian future, 16-year-old Katniss volunteers to take her younger sister’s place in a battle where children must fight to stay alive.

550826.title: The Hunger Games: Catching Fire
550826.description: As Katniss and Peeta embark on their victory tour, President Snow plans an even deadlier new Hunger Games, which threatens the future of Panem.

550828.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part 2
550828.description: The celebrated movie series reaches its epic climax, as the brave Katniss fights to liberate Panem's citizens in a final showdown with President Snow.

551255.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part 1
551255.description: The franchise phenomenon continues, as Katniss, having survived The Hunger Games, rises with District 13 to battle the oppressive President Snow.

555641.title: RV
555641.description: In the spirit of bonding with his dysfunctional family, patriarch Bob rents a motorhome for what becomes a madcap road trip to the Colorado Rockies.

557221.title: Cop Out
557221.description: Bruce Willis and Tracy Morgan star as an oddball pair of NYPD partners who must take on a ruthless, memorabilia-obsessed criminal.

563036.title: Bad Company
563036.description: When his identical twin brother is killed in the line of duty, a streetwise punk is recruited by a CIA agent to stop an arms deal from going bad.

563040.title: Dead Presidents
563040.description: A Vietnam War veteran returns home and is drawn into a life of crime when he pulls off a daring armored car robbery with a group of fellow vets.

563166.title: 28 Weeks Later
563166.description: Six months after the military declares Britain safe from the mysterious rage virus that ravaged the nation, a terrifying new nightmare soon begins.

563168.title: Predators
563168.description: A mercenary reluctantly leads a group of elite warriors mysteriously brought together on a jungle planet where they are hunted by an alien race.

571078.title: Obsessed
571078.description: A happily married businessman finds his life in shambles after a woman pursues him relentlessly, putting his wife in a dangerous predicament.

573585.title: Journey 2: The Mysterious Island
573585.description: When a young man receives his grandfather’s distress signal from a remote island, he heads off with his stepfather and a helicopter tour team.

581905.title: Little Nicky
581905.description: After Satan refuses to retire his post in Hell, he sends the nicest and youngest of his sons to New York City to bring his two renegade brothers home.

581920.title: Queen of the Damned
581920.description: After a century of sleep, the vampire Lestat takes up as the frontman for an undead rock band while unwittingly awakening the dangerous Queen Akasha.

589063.title: The Specialist
589063.description: An ex-CIA explosives expert with his own dark past helps a seductive beauty avenge the murder of her parents by a powerful Cuban-American crime boss.

589172.title: Secondhand Lions
589172.description: Set in the 1960s, this is the story of a 14-year-old’s amazing summer with his unusual uncles, as they tell him tales of their younger days.

589375.title: Tango & Cash
589375.description: A pair of rival LAPD cops become unlikely allies when both are framed and imprisoned on drug charges that force them in cahoots to clear their names.

591015.title: Proud Mary
591015.description: Taraji P. Henson stars as a steely hit woman working for a local Mob family who finds a protective instinct for a little boy while out for a kill.

591107.title: The House Bunny
591107.description: A former Playboy model finds a new path in life when she becomes an unlikely mentor and role model to a sorority full of studious young college students.

593866.title: Baby Boy
593866.description: The classic John Singleton film about a 20-year-old in South Central L.A. who loves like a man but isn’t stepping up in real life as a grown adult.

595396.description: Tells the story of how Spartan King Leonidas and his soldiers numbering just 300 beat King Xerxes of Persia, with an army of hundreds of thousands.

599603.title: Contagion
599603.description: Oscar®-winning filmmaker Steven Soderbergh (Ocean's Eleven films, Traffic) returns to large-scale cinema with this global action thriller that revolves around the threat of a deadly outbreak of a fatal disease and the people determined to keep it at bay. As the fast-moving epidemic grows, the worldwide medical community races to find a cure and control the panic that spreads faster than the virus itself. At the same time, ordinary people struggle to survive in a society coming apart. A stellar international ensemble cast including Academy Award® winners Matt Damon, Gwyneth Paltrow, Kate Winslet, Marion Cotillard and nominees Jude Law and Laurence Fishburne portray the dedicated doctors at the CDC and World Health Organization who rush to contain the outbreak of a new virus. Tracking its source to Hong Kong and searching for a cure, these determined Samaritans do their utmost to limit deaths, civil unrest and the false rumors surrounding the disease in this viral outbreak drama with multiple plot lines in the style of Soderbergh's Oscar®-winning narcotics drama Traffic.

599629.title: Eyes Wide Shut
599629.description: Tom Cruise and Nicole Kidman star as a married couple entangled in an intricate web of jealousy and sexual obsession in Stanley Kubrick's final cinematic offering.  At a Christmas party hosted by wealthy, unconventional Victor Ziegler (Sydney Pollack), provocative advances and innocent flirtations arouse suspicion as high-society physician Dr. William Harford (Cruise) and his sexy wife, Alice (Kidman) watch each other from a distance. Alone later, this seemingly perfect couple confront their intimate sexual fantasies--which don't include each other.  Caught between reality and illusion, jealousy and obsession, William struggles with his inner urges. Will he act on his erotic fantasies or keep them hidden deep inside? Sometimes a man can see more clearly with his Eyes Wide Shut.

599994.title: Two Weeks Notice
599994.description: For five years Lucy has been treated more like a nanny than a Harvard-trained lawyer, chosen George's clothes, arranged his divorce, lost sleep and gained an ulcer, but now she's calling it quits. She gives George her Two Weeks Notice.  George finally agrees to let her go ... if she finds her own replacement. After a challenging search, Lucy hires an ambitious young lawyer with an obvious eye for her new boss. Now, as she joins her devoted boyfriend for an adventure at sea, Lucy is finally free of George. Or is she? With Lucy sailing out of his life, George must decide if it's ever too late to say "I love you."

599997.title: Wedding Crashers
599997.description: Owen Wilson (Starsky & Hutch) and Vince Vaughn (Old School) star as John Beckwith and Jeremy Klein, two partying divorce attorneys--and committed womanizers--who have figured out a surefire way to meet women: they crash weddings. But the guys' happy-go-lucky lives change abruptly when John unexpectedly falls in love with a bridesmaid (Rachel McAdams - The Notebook). Things become even more complicated when the men discover that the object of John's affection is the daughter of the United States Secretary of the Treasury (Christopher Walken - Catch Me If You Can) in the engaging romantic comedy Wedding Crashers.

600021.title: Striptease
600021.description: For her most daring role ever, Demi Moore bares all in this erotic satire about a single mother who turns to stripping in a Miami nightclub to earn money for a child-custody battle. But her sensual dancing attracts the unwanted attention of a deranged congressman who will stop at nothing--even murder--to possess her.

601303.title: Hall Pass
601303.description: A pair of pals feeling restless in their otherwise happy marriages are given the green light to sleep with as many women as they can in one week.

602292.title: Blade
602292.description: A vampire-human hybrid uses his advanced powers and an arsenal of weapons to do battle with the bloodsucking monsters who threaten the living.

607451.title: E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial
607451.description: A boy forms a special bond with a sweet and gifted alien from another planet. He tries to keep it a secret, but he needs help to keep the visitor safe.

607952.title: True Lies
607952.description: A deadly and talented spy for the government hides his dangerous day job from his family, but his secret heroics take a toll on his marriage.

609721.title: The Karate Kid
609721.description: Jaden Smith stars in the 2010 reboot of the iconic franchise, this time as a young arrival in China who learns self-defense from a karate master.

610528.title: Blade Trinity
610528.description: An all-star sequel featuring Ryan Reynolds and Jessica Biel as vampire hunters who join Blade to stop a virus from being unleashed on the undead.

610572.title: Goodfellas
610572.description: Based on a true story, a young man rises up the ranks of a mob family over several years, dabbling in drugs, heists and murders along the way.

611206.title: The 13th Warrior
611206.description: Far from home, an exiled ambassador joins a fierce band of Viking warriors, who are attacked by ferocious creatures that devour every living thing.

612777.title: The Kitchen
612777.description: Set in 1978 Hell's Kitchen, this is the story of three housewives whose mobster husbands are sent to prison, leaving them to handle business.

616504.title: Bring It On: Again
616504.description: In this sassy sequel, a new squad of cheerleaders takes on the establishment in a winner-takes-all competition filled with spunk, smarts and spirit.

616506.title: Bring It On: In It to Win It
616506.description: Hot music, high-flyin' fun and no-holds-barred competition reach new heights when the East Coast Jets take on their rivals, the West Coast Sharks!

616508.title: Bring It On: Worldwide #Cheersmack
616508.description: The Rebels are challenged to a cheer showdown for squads from all around the world. Cheer Goddess (Vivica A. Fox) organizes the virtual battle.

616510.title: Bring It On: Fight to the Finish
616510.description: Get ready for more hot music, fierce competition and high-flyin’ fun in Bring It On: Fight to the Finish starring Christina Milian.

616516.title: Bring It On: All or Nothing
616516.description: When a popular cheerleader moves from her posh neighborhood to a working-class one, she soon finds herself at odds with her new classmates.

617284.title: A Low Down Dirty Shame
617284.description: A disgraced LAPD cop-turned private eye teams up with a DEA agent in a search for $20 million in stolen cash and the drug kingpin who ended his career.

617447.title: Pretty Woman
617447.description: Julia Roberts stars as a witty prostitute who charms a serious businessman, as the two unlikely lovers fall for each other over the course of a week.

622678.title: Water for Elephants
622678.description: During the Great Depression, a veterinary student, recently orphaned and suddenly adrift, joins the circus and falls for the animal trainer’s wife.

622846.title: Australia
622846.description: With the threat of war looming, a landowner in Australia fights to keep her cattle and her land with the help of a seasoned ranch hand.

625256.title: First Sunday
625256.description: Two bumbling criminals discover they haven't got a prayer when they attempt to steal from the local church.

628023.title: The Best Little Whorehouse in Texas
628023.description: This rousing musical portrays a sheriff and a madam, who band together to save the infamous Texas Chicken Ranch from a big-city TV crusader.

628970.title: Hellboy II: The Golden Army
628970.description: Hellboy and his crew of paranormal outcasts face off with forces of darkness in this imaginative adventure from visionary director Guillermo del Toro.

630919.title: Major Payne
630919.description: In peacetime, a major with a lust for war is discharged from the Marine Corps and reduced to training a group of misfit ROTC cadets at a prep school.

630921.title: The Last House on the Left
630921.description: After their daughter is raped and left for dead, a couple exact bloody revenge on the attackers who have unknowingly taken shelter at their home.

637106.title: Unknown
637106.description: A man awakens from a coma after a car wreck to find his wife doesn’t recognize him, his identity has been stolen, and hitmen are trying to kill him.

638331.title: Cowboys & Aliens
638331.description: “Iron Man” director Jon Favreau directed this sci-fi Western with Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford squaring off against a massive intergalactic threat.

639561.title: The Waterboy
639561.description: A socially awkward but well-meaning water boy's violent temper tantrums inspire a football coach to train him as his team’s defensive tackle.

639782.title: Ninja Assassin
639782.description: After a trained ninja leaves behind his former life, he works with a Europol agent to take down the hired killers who taught him everything he knows.

642282.title: Escape Room
642282.description: When three couples celebrate a 30th birthday with an escape room, they quickly realize that the game is deadly, and only winners survive.

643528.title: Beaches
643528.description: A lifelong friendship between two women, one a demure, privileged socialite, the other a bold, struggling singer, takes unexpected twists and turns.

647464.title: Hide and Seek
647464.description: In the wake of his wife’s suicide, a psychiatrist becomes powerless to help his young daughter cope as she turns to what began as an imaginary friend.

647476.title: Aliens in the Attic
647476.description: With their parents none the wiser, siblings must stop a band of tiny aliens from invading the basement of their vacation home and conquering Earth.

647479.title: Sister Act 2: Back in the Habit
647479.description: A Las Vegas showgirl-turned-singing nun becomes a run-down Catholic school’s only hope of reviving its music program and keeping its doors open.

647690.title: What About Bob?
647690.description: A month-long family vacation in New Hampshire becomes a psychiatrist’s undoing when his most dependent patient tracks him down at his rental property.

651086.title: Hancock
651086.description: A sarcastic, hard-living, misunderstood superhero, whose antics caused him to fall out of favor with the public, saves someone who might save him.

651094.title: Lake Placid
651094.description: At a serene Maine lake, a 30-foot reptilian eating machine hungers for a fragile paleontologist on her first field assignment and a tasty billionaire.

651120.title: The Tourist
651120.description: An American tourist visiting Italy to mend a broken heart is seduced by a beautiful woman, who ensnares him in an international criminal plot.

655363.title: We Bought a Zoo
655363.description: A single dad set out to give his family a fresh start by uprooting them to the Southern California country to a home in the middle of a neglected zoo.

657674.title: The Edge
657674.description: A plane crash in the Alaskan wilderness pits two enemies and a billionaire against a blood-thirsty Kodiak bear in a brutal struggle for survival.

659846.title: Waiting...
659846.description: A group of young employees at a chain restaurant ponder their lives while dealing with annoying patrons and staving off boredom with antics.

661142.title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
661142.description: The third film in the Twilight franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders.

661144.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn: Part 1
661144.description: The fourth film in the Twilight franchise. A marriage, honeymoon and child bring unforeseen and shocking developments for Bella and Edward.

663215.title: How High
663215.description: Silas and Jamal are two slackers who beat the odds and get accepted to Harvard, where they turn the school upside down with their pursuit of parties.

664191.title: Double Take
664191.description: An investment banker on the run swipes the passport of a petty thief, thus swapping identities, in this comic urban take on the Prince and the Pauper.

664749.title: 10 Things I Hate About You
664749.description: On the first day at his new school, Cameron instantly falls for Bianca, the gorgeous girl of his dreams. The only problem? She isn't allowed to date.

665462.title: Apollo 13
665462.description: A routine space flight becomes a desperate battle of survival in this breathtaking and true-story of adventure, courage, and faith.

667422.title: Pacific Rim
667422.description: With alien invaders rising from the sea, a washed-up former pilot and an untested trainee use massive robots to combat the apocalyptic threat.

670370.title: Brightburn
670370.description: What if a child from another world crash-landed on Earth, but instead of becoming a hero to mankind, he proved to be something far more sinister?

672287.title: The Angry Birds Movie
672287.description: When mysterious green piggies visit an island populated by flightless birds, it's up to three unlikely outcasts to figure out what the pigs are up to.

672301.title: The 40-Year-Old Virgin
672301.description: Nice guy Andy has lived his whole life without "doing it." Now, his misguided pals are helping him reverse his fortunes—and maybe even find true love.

672442.title: Dredd
672442.description: The head of Mega City One’s elite police force becomes the city’s last hope when a sex worker-turned-drug dealer aims to take over the city.

680735.title: Jason X
680735.description: Cryogenically frozen in the 21st century and left on an inhabitable Earth, the hockey-masked killer is thawed in 2455 for a new reign of terror.

682797.title: Casper
682797.description: Seeing is believing in this adventure about a kind spirit in need of a friend and his ghostly uncles who want all “fleshies” out of their manor.

684884.title: Don't Breathe
684884.description: A group of teens breaks into a blind man's home, thinking they'll get away with the perfect crime but get more than they bargained for once inside.

686278.title: Doom
686278.description: Based on the hit videogame, this adventure begins when a call for help from a research station on Mars sends a team of mercenary Marines into action.

686285.title: Honey 3: Dare to Dance
686285.description: After losing her place at a prestigious academy, a struggling dancer puts everything on the line to produce a hip-hop adaptation of Romeo and Juliet.

686287.title: Honey 4: Rise Up and Dance
686287.description: A street dancer comes out of the shadow of her trained dancer sister and enters a dance competition with the prize being a college scholarship.

686449.title: Honey
686449.description: Pulse-pounding music and awesome dance moves ignite this exhilarating story of one dancer’s passion, courage and determination to follow her dreams.

686450.title: Honey 2
686450.description: After a brush with the law, Maria returns to her Bronx roots with nothing but a talent for street dance and a burning ambition to prove herself.

694011.title: Vice
694011.description: This acclaimed biopic explores how Dick Cheney quietly wielded immense power as George W. Bush's Vice President, reshaping the U.S. and the globe.

694144.title: Godzilla
694144.description: When a giant monster created by nuclear tests descends upon New York, it's up to the U.S. Army and an odd team of investigators to stop the creature.

694229.title: American Pie Presents: Band Camp
694229.description: Get ready for the antics when Stifler’s younger brother spends a summer encountering camp counselors, hidden cameras, and a pair of Playmates.

694233.title: American Pie Presents: The Book of Love
694233.description: With the help of the legendary Book of Love, three friends embark on an outrageous quest to lose their virginity with the girls of their dreams.

694577.title: American Reunion
694577.description: The whole American Pie gang returns to East Great Falls, Michigan to make their reunion into the most outrageous weekend since high school.

694581.title: American Pie Presents: Beta House
694581.description: Get ready for the most outrageous freshman year in collegiate history as Dwight Stifler, his cousin Erik, and Jim’s dad pledge a wild fraternity.

694702.title: American Wedding
694702.description: When Jim and Michelle decide it's time to tie the knot, the gang celebrates this rite of passage with a wild bachelor party accompanied by Jim's dad.

694768.title: American Pie
694768.description: The stakes are high when four friends make the pact to lose their virginity by prom night in this romp about high school, band camp and apple pie.

695015.title: American Pie Presents: The Naked Mile
695015.description: Erik Stifler, his devoted friends and some uninhibited sorority girls take the chance of their lives at the annual and infamous Naked Mile race.

695341.title: Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married Too?
695341.description: Four couples on an annual retreat struggle to save their marriages while each of them battles their own financial, physical and emotional issues.

696058.title: American Pie 2
696058.description: A year after their prom night misadventures, the gang reunites for a summer they'll never forget at a beach house they turn into party central.

698128.title: Running With the Devil
698128.description: A tenacious federal agent traces the supply line of a ring of experienced cocaine dealers, as two cartel envoys hunt for a shipment lost in transit.

698959.title: Repo Men
698959.description: After being outfitted with a top-of-the-line heart replacement, an organ repo man must go on the run when he finds himself unable to pay for it.

707103.title: Blazing Saddles
707103.description: A corrupt governor will grant a reprieve to a convict under one condition: the condemned man agrees to serve as sheriff of a small Western town.

712892.title: Hope Floats
712892.description: After learning about her husband's affair, a former beauty queen moves back to her tiny Texas hometown and reunites with an old flame.

720943.title: Burlesque
720943.description: A small-town singer moves to the city for a chance at fame when she finds a glamorous nightclub packed with dancers and an owner in need of a star.

720947.title: Little Man
720947.description: After a stolen diamond gets stashed in the home of a husband and wife, a pint-sized jewel thief poses as the world's ugliest baby to get it back.

723250.title: Bend It Like Beckham
723250.description: Despite the wishes of their traditional families, two young women from different walks of life aim for a career in professional soccer.

723254.title: Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World
723254.description: A distinguished young captain of the British Navy leads his crew on a mission to take a French vessel with a reputation for sinking British ships.

723256.title: Red Sparrow
723256.description: A Russian intelligence officer tasked with seducing a CIA agent finds her mission and its objective threatened when they both fall for each other.

723505.title: The Ladykillers
723505.description: An eccentric Southern professor and his crew pose as a band in order to rob a casino, all under the nose of his unsuspecting landlord.

724149.title: Celtic Pride
724149.description: Jimmy and Mike are a pair of die-hard basketball fans who'd do anything to help their team win, even if it means kidnapping the opposing star player!

724347.title: The Best Man
724347.description: A Chicago author forces his old friend group to confront secrets from the past when he arrives in town for his best friend’s wedding with a new book.

100000001.title: Kubo and the Two Strings
100000001.description: After accidentally summoning an evil spirit, Kubo must recover his fallen samurai father’s mystical weaponry and discover his own magical powers.

100000171.title: Bohemian Rhapsody
100000171.description: Celebrates the rock band Queen, their music and their extraordinary frontman in the years leading up to their appearance at 1985's Live Aid concert.

100000302.title: Real Steel
100000302.description: In a near future where human boxers have been replaced by robots, a struggling ex-boxer and his estranged son reunite while training a robot fighter.

100000320.title: Taken 2
100000320.description: When retired CIA operative Brian Mills and his wife are taken hostage by a vengeful gang leader, they must rely on their daughter's help to escape.

100000379.title: Classmates
100000379.description: A computer mixup gives two college freshman the chance to swap places but things take a turn when the switch puts them both in danger.

100000439.title: Semi-Pro
100000439.description: In 1970s Michigan, the coach of a rag-tag basketball team pulls out all the stops to get his team into the NBA before their league dissolves.

100000480.title: Bad Teacher
100000480.description: A foul-mouthed seventh grade teacher begrudgingly returns to work so that she can pay for breast implants after being dumped by her sugar daddy.

100000487.title: Ghostbusters II
100000487.description: The superstars of the supernatural reunite to battle an enormous underground river of slime that threatens New York City in this hilarious sequel.

100000784.title: Ghostbusters
100000784.description: A trio of failed university parapsychologists cash in on an uptick in New Yorkers’ paranormal complaints by setting up a ghost extermination service.

100000963.title: Blood, Sweat and Cheer
100000963.description: A mother seeking to relive her glory days poses as her teen daughter to join a high school dance team.

100001075.title: The Adventures of Rocky and Bullwinkle
100001075.description: This live-action adventure features everyone's favorite moose and squirrel in a fun-filled race to foil a scheme to destroy the world!

100001394.title: Carnifex
100001394.description: On their quest into the Australian Outback to track the animals left displaced by bushfires, a trio discovers a terrifying species and realize they're the ones being tracked.

100001593.title: Shaft
100001593.description: After his friend’s untimely death, cyber security expert John Shaft Jr. teams up with his estranged father to search the city’s criminal underbelly.

100001725.title: Mindcage
100001725.description: Two detectives must strike a deal with a brilliant serial killer on death row who turned his victims into art exhibits when a copycat killer strikes.

100001799.title: The Raid
100001799.description: When the government’s Armed Offenders Squad launches a raid in his backyard, a local Māori cop must decide which side he will protect and serve. Based on true events.

100001827.title: The Air Up There
100001827.description: A basketball coach travels to Africa to recruit a new star, but before he returns home, he must help the player’s tribe defeat an evil mining company.

100001829.title: Dr. Dolittle 2
100001829.description: Dr. Dolittle is back! This time around, he’s playing matchmaker for a lovesick circus bear and helping a community of forest animals save their home.

100001830.title: The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy
100001830.description: Seconds before Earth is destroyed to make way for a new hyperspace express route, a mild-mannered man is whisked off to an intergalactic odyssey.

100001831.title: Jungle 2 Jungle
100001831.description: When a Manhattan banker learns that he has a son being raised in the Amazon, he brings the boy to the city to experience life in the concrete jungle.

100001832.title: Man of the House
100001832.description: In an effort to impress the disapproving son of the woman of his dreams, a U.S. Justice Department lawyer decides to join the YMCA Indian Guides.

100001834.title: Mighty Joe Young
100001834.description: A 15-foot gorilla is removed from his habitat in Africa and brought to California where he falls victim to poachers, promoters and conservationists.

100001835.title: The Old Man & the Gun
